Content:: Branko Cvejić (Serbian Cyrillic: Бранко Цвејић; 25 August 1946 – 26 July 2022) was a Serbian actor. He appeared in more than one hundred films from 1962 onwards.[1] Cvejić was director of the Yugoslav Drama Theatre.[2]  This article about a Serbian actor is a stub. You can help Wikipedia by expanding it.
